name: Rainy Vacation
description:
Have you ever traveled for vacation to do outdoor activities but then realize the weathermen made the wrong prediction for the weekend? That's exactly what happened the first night out in Vegas. But when life gives you rain have a Martini. A Candy Martini.

1/6 'Candy Martini Bar Collection.' 

Collectors must collect 6/6 different art pieces of the Candy Martini Bar Collection to get the 'Big Shot' NFT transferred to them at no cost.
